results.name: Mental Health
results.description: The state of psychological and emotional well-being.

subConcepts.name: Mindfulness
subConcepts.description: Paying attention in a particular way: on purpose, in the present moment, and non-judgmentally.

subConcepts.name: Cognitive Health
subConcepts.description: The ability to think, learn, remember, and reason.

results.name: Emotional Health
results.description: The ability to understand, manage, and express your emotions in healthy ways.

subConcepts.name: Emotional Regulation
subConcepts.description: The ability to control or reframe one's emotional responses.

subConcepts.name: Self-Awareness
subConcepts.description: Understanding one's own emotions, strengths, weaknesses, and values.

results.name: Social Health
results.description: The ability to connect and form meaningful relationships with others.

results.name: Spiritual Health
results.description: A sense of purpose, meaning, and connection to something larger than oneself.
